      "date": "2013-07-12 09:33:09.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/5db75dcc-ead3-11e2-847f-52540035b04c).  Ran 15 tests.  No failures.",
