      "date": "2013-07-12 11:44:30.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/d26ecd64-eae5-11e2-847f-52540035b04c).  Ran 17 tests.  3 tests failed: runtests, conf-sanity, replay-single.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
